The Snyder Cut:

+ Way better than the original mess.
+¬†Better character building.
+ Better Steppenwolf.
+ Kept me entertained.
+ Letos Joker looked better.
- Too long.
-¬†Script was sketchy.
- Weightless action.
- Story is still too messy.
- Not enough Willem Dafoe.
#SnydersCut
